steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"2t7ep","text":"Weigh 2g of Eosin Y disodium salt and place it into a 1000mL Earlenmyer flask","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"99gnn","text":"Measure 40mL of dionized water and add it to the flask. Swirl to dissolve Eosin powder. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"8dip2","text":"Measure 160mL of 95% ethanol and add it to the flask. Swirl to dissolve. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"8mpme","text":"Using a p1000 Pipette, add 1mL (1000uL) of Glacial Acetic acid to the solution. Swirl until homogeneous.  ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
